camp/barracks/battalion/to build/to operate/to manage/to strive for
to set up camp/Taiwan pr. [an1 ying2 zha2 zhai4]

sentences.english: The Israelites moved on and camped at Oboth.
sentences.chinese: 以色列人起行，安营在阿伯。

sentences.english: They had encamped among the thick grass.
And they took their journey from Succoth， and encamped in Etham， in the edge of the wilderness.
sentences.chinese: 他们从疏割起行，在旷野边的以倘安营。

sentences.english: We pitched camp in a river valley.
The families of the sons of Kohath shall pitch on the side of the tabernacle southward.
sentences.chinese: 哥辖儿子的诸族要在帐幕的南边安营。

sentences.english: And they removed from Benejaakan, and encamped at Horhagidgad.
sentences.chinese: 从比尼亚干起行，安营在曷哈及甲。

sentences.english: They left the Red Sea and camped in the Desert of Sin.
sentences.chinese: 从红海边起行，安营在汛的旷野。

sentences.english: And they removed from Benejaakan， and encamped at Horhagidgad.
sentences.chinese: 从比尼亚干起行，安营在曷哈及甲。

sentences.english: They left Rephidim and camped in the Desert of Sinai.
sentences.chinese: 从利非订起行，安营在西奈的旷野。

sentences.english: And they departed from Rephidim， and pitched in the wilderness of Sinai.
sentences.chinese: 从利非订起行，安营在西奈的旷野。

sentences.english: And afterward the people removed from Hazeroth, and pitched in the wilderness of Paran.
sentences.chinese: 以后百姓从哈洗录起行，在巴兰的旷野安营。

sentences.english: Take breaks and camp away from trails and other visitors.
sentences.chinese: 憩息或安营时远离步道与其他游人。

sentences.english: And they departed from Oboth， and pitched in Ijeabarim， in the border of Moab.
sentences.chinese: 从阿伯起行，安营在以耶亚巴琳，摩押的边界。

sentences.english: The construction crew set camp at the specified place.
sentences.chinese: 建筑队在指定地点安营扎寨。

sentences.english: Next Abimelech went to Thebez and besieged it and captured it.
sentences.chinese: 亚比米勒到提备斯，向提备斯安营，就攻取了那城。

sentences.english: And they removed from Jotbathah， and encamped at Ebronah.
sentences.chinese: 从约巴他起行，安营在阿博拿。
